				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3>What is the cheapest plastic surgery procedure in India?</h3>
					<p>Liposuction for a single area is among the more affordable plastic surgery procedures in India, with costs starting from approximately INR 50,000. However, the best procedure for you depends on your individual goals, not just the price. A consultation with Dr. Johar will help determine the most appropriate and cost-effective option for your needs.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3>Are there hidden costs in plastic surgery?</h3>
					<p>At Dr. Johar's clinic, there are no hidden costs. Our cost estimate includes the surgeon's fee, anesthesia, facility charges, pre-operative tests, and post-operative follow-up visits. Any additional costs, such as compression garments or medications, will be clearly communicated upfront.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3>Can I pay for plastic surgery in installments?</h3>
					<p>Yes, many clinics including Dr. Johar's offer EMI options that allow you to spread the cost over several months. We partner with leading financial institutions to provide flexible, low-interest payment plans. During your consultation, we will discuss the available options.</p>
